</category>

<category>
    <pattern>WHAT IS A DUMBBELL</pattern>
    <template>A dumbbell is a short handheld weight used for strength training. It can be used one at a time or as a pair for many exercises.</template>
</category>

<category>
    <pattern>WHAT IS DUMBBELL</pattern>
    <template>A dumbbell is a short handheld weight used for strength training. It can be used one at a time or as a pair for many exercises.</template>
</category>

<category>
    <pattern>WHAT IS A BARBELL</pattern>
    <template>A barbell is a long metal bar used for weight training exercises such as squats, deadlifts, bench press, rows, and overhead press.</template>
</category>

<category>
    <pattern>WHAT IS BARBELL</pattern>
    <template>A barbell is a long metal bar used for weight training exercises such as squats, deadlifts, bench press, rows, and overhead press.</template>
</category>

<category>
    <pattern>WHAT IS A KETTLEBELL</pattern>
    <template>A kettlebell is a round weight with a handle. It is used for swings, goblet squats, presses, carries, and other strength and conditioning exercises.</template>
</category>

<category>
    <pattern>WHAT IS KETTLEBELL</pattern>
